long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
History Webhook - Track Browser History with Ease

Description:
'History Webhook' is a simple yet powerful Chrome extension designed for users who need to monitor browser navigation events seamlessly. Every time you navigate to a new page, 'History Webhook' automatically sends an HTTP request. This can be customized to your preferences, commonly directed to localhost:12345. Whether you're a developer, a data analyst, or just someone curious about your browsing patterns, this tool provides a straightforward solution to keep track of your digital footprints.

Features:

    Automatic HTTP Requests: Sends an HTTP request with each browser history event.
    Customizable URL Endpoint: Easily configure the URL to your specific needs.
    User-Friendly Interface: Designed for simplicity and ease of use.
    Efficient Tracking: Ideal for local development and testing environments.

'History Webhook' offers a seamless way to integrate browser history tracking into your workflow. Install now and take control of your browsing data!
